聚合子查询提升后，支持带 cast 的非基表条件下推
EXPLAIN select * from t2 where id = (select max(qzkh_id) from t1 where mphone = RIGHT(FROM_BASE64(remark_name), 11));
Query Plan
========================================================
|ID|OPERATOR              |NAME  |EST.ROWS|EST.TIME(us)|
--------------------------------------------------------
|0 |NESTED-LOOP JOIN      |      |1       |273         |
|1 |├─TABLE FULL SCAN     |t2    |1       |3           |
|2 |└─SUBPLAN SCAN        |VIEW1 |1       |270         |
|3 |  └─MERGE GROUP BY    |      |1       |270         |
|4 |    └─TABLE RANGE SCAN|t1(i1)|98      |268         |
========================================================
Outputs & filters:
-------------------------------------
  0 - output([t2.id], [t2.remark_name]), filter(nil), rowset=256
      conds(nil), nl_params_([t2.id(:0)], [t2.remark_name(:1)]), use_batch=false
  1 - output([t2.remark_name], [t2.id]), filter(nil), rowset=256
      access([t2.remark_name], [t2.id]), partitions(p0)
      is_index_back=false, is_global_index=false, 
      range_key([t2.__pk_increment]), range(MIN ; MAX)always true
  2 - output(nil), filter([:0 = VIEW1.max(qzkh_id)]), rowset=256
      access([VIEW1.max(qzkh_id)])
  3 - output([T_FUN_MAX(t1.qzkh_id)], [cast(t1.mphone, VARCHAR(1048576))]), filter(nil), rowset=256
      group(nil), agg_func([T_FUN_MAX(t1.qzkh_id)])
  4 - output([t1.qzkh_id], [cast(t1.mphone, VARCHAR(1048576))]), filter([cast(t1.mphone, VARCHAR(1048576)) = right(FROM_BASE64(cast(:1, VARCHAR(1048576))),
       11)]), rowset=256
      access([t1.__pk_increment], [t1.mphone], [t1.qzkh_id]), partitions(p0)
      is_index_back=true, is_global_index=false, filter_before_indexback[true], 
      range_key([t1.mphone], [t1.__pk_increment]), range(MIN,MIN ; MAX,MAX)always true, 
      range_cond([cast(t1.mphone, VARCHAR(1048576)) = right(FROM_BASE64(cast(:1, VARCHAR(1048576))), 11)])
select * from t2 where id = (select max(qzkh_id) from t1 where mphone = RIGHT(FROM_BASE64(remark_name), 11));
+------+-------------+
| id   | remark_name |
+------+-------------+
+------+-------------+
写在 select 里，子查询能走索引，默认不做聚合子查询提升
EXPLAIN select (select max(qzkh_id) from t1 where mphone = RIGHT(FROM_BASE64(remark_name), 11)) as c1 from t2;
