写在 select 里，子查询能走索引，强制 unnest 后能做非基表条件下推
EXPLAIN select (select /*+unnest*/ max(qzkh_id) from t1 where mphone = RIGHT(FROM_BASE64(remark_name), 11)) as c1 from t2;
